==Post-election== [[Günther Oettinger]] stayed on Minister-President, in a CDU-FDP coalition, after a CDU-Green coalition had also been considered (for the first time in this state).
On 27 November 2007 [[Oswald Metzger]], elected in [[Biberach an der Riß|Biberach]], formally ended his membership in the [[Alliance '90/The Greens]], but stayed in the Landtag without a faction until, on 18 February 2008, [[Eugen Schlachter]] (member of [[Alliance '90/The Greens]]) took his seat, thus bringing the Greens faction to 17 seats again. Metzger then joined the CDU.
